 when I was - thirteen I left school. I went - as an apprentice dressmaker for two years for nothing. And then of course - I had to be in bed - when I was that old - when I was thirteen - and fourteen.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid12675217 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid11631485\charrsid865768 You still had to be in bed by eight o'clock?
