d a - my uncle was a - councilor. My great-uncle was a magistrate. And that's all I can tell you about that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid12675217 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid11631485\charrsid865768 Can you tell me about them then?
