y were relations of my father's. Yes. There was - Henry Toms, he was a - he was a - councilor. And - he was in business too, and he was in the - pottery business too. My Uncle Henry was. And then Mr Edwin Brookfields, he was a magistrate, and he was a big
 man in the town. And - his photograph was in {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname place}}{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname PlaceName}}Longton{\*\xmlclose} {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname PlaceType}}Town Hall{\*\xmlclose}{\*\xmlclose}
, I think it is now. Over one of the doors upstairs.
